CustomField.description: The range field should define the page range of the document being defined. Page ranges can be defined with a mixture of comma separated lists of page numbers and/or ranges using hyphens (ex: 1,2,5-8).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The range field should define the page range of the document being defined. Page ranges can be defined with a mixture of comma separated lists of page numbers and/or ranges using hyphens (ex: 1,2,5-8).
CustomField.label: Page Range
